ai-ja220:1.2_0: I’ve gone forth in the country of his wife.
ai-ja220:1.4_0: like an elephant in a womb.
ai-ja220:2.2_0: I’ve gone forth in the country of his wife.
ai-ja220:2.4_0: like a moth in a dollar,
ai-ja220:2.5_0: recollecting the teaching of the good.
ai-ja220:3.1_0: was born to the tenth Dhamma.
ai-ja220:3.2_0: The seventh sub-chapter on arms is finished.
ai-ja220:5.1_0: Then a fond of Bāhiya and Robe,
ai-ja220:5.4_0: with a thousand dollars, whips, and swords.
